title: Spider-Man vs. Wolverine (1987, Minutemen-Dogma)
description: Pretty much what it sounds like - to celebrate Marvel's 25th anniversary, they got arguably their two most popular and famous heroes to slug it out in this one-shot special. Spidey is in the black symbiote costume, if you want an idea of when this took place. Mostly a pure slug fest with some good art, and a servicable hook by James Owsley. Thanks to Minutemen-Dogma for the awesome scan, please seed and enjoy! :-)
